cover, and I wouldn't pick up another book,

00:18:17.400 --> 00:18:19.890
Marissa, until I finished that book.

00:18:19.890 --> 00:18:21.280
And I knew I was finished with it.

00:18:21.280 --> 00:18:27.710
But now, with the tablet, you can just -- you
can put in any number, hundreds and hundreds

00:18:27.710 --> 00:18:32.360
of books, and just pick up where you left
off on any number of books, and it's a very

00:18:32.360 --> 00:18:33.360
-- it's confusing.

00:18:33.360 --> 00:18:34.360
[ Laughter ]
&gt;&gt;Marissa Mayer: It's confusing and convenient.

00:18:34.360 --> 00:18:36.150
But I'm the same way.

00:18:36.150 --> 00:18:38.710
&gt;&gt;Martha Stewart: It's very convenient.

00:18:38.710 --> 00:18:39.710
But it is confusing.

00:18:39.710 --> 00:18:43.710
&gt;&gt;Marissa Mayer: But it is nice to be actually
able to jump around between the books.

